description:
With the Zapp application, make your everyday life easier. Zapp enables easy ordering and fast food delivery. Choose your favorite restaurant and enjoy delicious dishes.

How to place an order with the Zapp application:
1. Register;
2. Specify your address;
3. Choose a restaurant or shop and choose a dish or groceries;
4. Choose the payment method (cash/card);
5. Follow the delivery driver live;
6. Rate the restaurant and the delivery driver;
7. Enjoy!

Advantages of the Zapp application:
1. Simple use of the application;
2. Real-time driver tracking;
3. Picking up an order in a restaurant/store;
4. The possibility of scheduling delivery for a certain time;
5. Card payment;
6. Actions and promotions;
7. Branded vehicles and professional drivers.

Our mission and vision are user-oriented, and we are constantly working to improve the service and the application because the user experience is very important to us.
